{
  "stem": "27335.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, we knew-- well, we knew that we were going overseas and there was going to be further things.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We just had the ground training, the-- the-- the initial training for parachute jumping because they haven't had that.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Coming a couple months later, then they had also parachute training in Orono area.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know if you noticed it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we just had a ground training from-- from a tower.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You jumped.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it was the same sensation as from-- from-- from-- from plane.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, the was a real fast ship.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had escort, better ships and fighting planes, all to-- pulled out about 4 o'clock in the-- in the afternoon.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the day-- the day was-- I don't know, I think it was-- it was Wednesday.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it escorted us out about-- about 300 miles or something.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then they just disappeared.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were on our own.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But then it took a detour and zig-zagging, zig-zagging up to North Atlantic, North Atlantic, because the German submarines weren't fast enough to catch up unless they knew the exact route of the ship and they were waiting in ambush.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But they were dangerous.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the survived the whole-- the whole war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Mind you, they destroyed 4,000 ships in the North Atlantic from the American borders, the Canadian ports-- ports, and Canadian ports.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
